aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你SAT拎到差唔多lv先講啦</blockquote><br />\nSAT無謂拎黎打飛機, 根本係記憶+速讀大賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a980e687c072553402571a4f946be2f9bdd1e70","tid":162251,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎大家都認為英文考試高分就代表英文好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n這就是香港教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班傻仔去到外國咪又係啞撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b087224ff2e96d1df77912efebd9126ffb182cc","tid":162251,"uid":87257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇普通話廢過英文<br />\n利申9成普通話聽唔明又唔識講</blockquote><br />\n唔係好正常咩"},{"pid":"0f9972c401f251525999a0d0d75e946ed6f46afa","tid":162251,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇黎大家都認為英文考試高分就代表英文好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n強國人考ielts/toefl等英文試或者SAT直頭爆晒分<br />\n但唔見得佢地英文真係好</blockquote><br />\n但樓上啲人又係咁拎啲分嚟比<br />\n就算考試中低過英都唔代表中文差過英文<br />\n<br />\n正路香港生活都無乜可能英好過中<br />\n除非係外藉人仕<br />\n<br />\n相反如果有人學第三種語言例如日，俄呢啲而自覺比英文好我反而覺得合理些少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相信香港絕對大把人日文好過英文<br />\n起碼多數人學日文既motivation係強, 而且有中文底學日文好易<br />\n俄文好過英文就難以置信d, 除非你話有俄妹女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0546b0e2706a31a75eaeeee2dee6d6f6318b5498","tid":162251,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"又係度批鬥自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c540a37ed4048974d9c569a4c2c1801e9383fa5","tid":162251,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike