樓上啲人又係咁拎啲分嚟比<br />\n就算考試中低過英都唔代表中文差過英文<br />\n<br />\n正路香港生活都無乜可能英好過中<br />\n除非係外藉人仕<br />\n<br />\n相反如果有人學第三種語言例如日，俄呢啲而自覺比英文好我反而覺得合理些少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相信香港絕對大把人日文好過英文<br />\n起碼多數人學日文既motivation係強, 而且有中文底學日文好易<br />\n俄文好過英文就難以置信d, 除非你話有俄妹女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日俄呢啲都係打個譬如啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要係好多人覺得香港考試英文高分過中文就代表自己英文好過中文<br />\n<br />\n不過我認同你所講香港絕對大把人日文好過英文<br />\n多數係地理同文化因素"},{"pid":"9939baaf0b96b4a95ee1d1dd23dc268618dd043d","tid":162251,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:33:32.000Z","msg":"I go to school by bus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c70b38121e3ffcb1275d3f7d15968855112ba1","tid":162251,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英文=私樓<br />\n中文=公屋</blockquote><br />\n咁德法西俄文？</blockquote><br />\n半山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIch spreche bisschen Deutsch.</blockquote><br />\nIch spreche ein bisschen Deutsch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n讀緊B2"},{"pid":"ca7bec41e5b4f4d841d4bf0fb7895ca35efa3848","tid":162251,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>me engrish is gooder than chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">my english</span> is <span style=\"color: red;\">better</span> than chinese</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">M</span>y <span style=\"color: red;\">E</span>nglish is better than <span style=\"color: red;\">my</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">C</span>hinese<span style=\"color: red;\">.</span>"},{"pid":"c8da4a8228e058b75cd0dfe3d0d30464e38d8ba3","tid":162251,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>me engrish is gooder than chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">my english</span> is <span style=\"color: red;\">better</span> than chinese</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">M</span>y <span style=\"color: red;\">E</span>nglish is better than <span style=\"color: red;\">my</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">C</span>hinese<span style=\"color: red;\">.</span></blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b366998fe37d33ceaf129c9a6105b2406d90395a","tid":162251,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為中文更差 唔好講考試呢d 成日都執筆忘字同搵唔到合適中文字去表達</blockquote><br />\n你可以十秒內將呢句譯做英文然後表達得比中文原句更好，就真係英文好過中文啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申，住左外國好耐，從來唔敢話自己英好過中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b5ed92e82dbadbc7be7cc072245f6f27c09d93","tid":162251,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好簡單，問返佢：你去到英國美國係咪同而家一樣可以對答如流先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你用中文講唔到一成嘅嘢要用英文代替，但講英文個陣睇撚死你最少八成唔識表達啦戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部份香港所謂英文好既人去到外國通常又聾又啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼佬真係同你全速講野再加勁多slangs，好多香港人聽都聽唔明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fddb49ccfc6e43527930d9ed4be363d12ed0f3","tid":162251,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:04:48.000Z","msg":"因為佢哋係垃圾，英文已經唔好，中文日日講都仲咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識啲bba law仔都唔會咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{